README

You will probably need to do some installations:

pip3 install --upgrade pip
pip3 install opencv-python
pip3 install editdistance
pip3 install tensorflow

pip3 install matplotlib
pip3 install networkx
pip3 install imutils


If you need, you can create a virtual environment :

python3 -m venv <path/to/your/virtual/env>


Activate it with :

source bin/activate

Then install all the modules given above.


Quit the environment with :

deactivate


For an example about how to use HTR, see "example.py" and run 
python3 example.py
from the /src directory
